LogicalOp - Interface in cl.uchile.dcc.scrabble.types
This interface contains Logical operations for Scr objects (binary and bool) It contains logic and, or & negation
logicAnd(LogicalOp) - Method in interface cl.uchile.dcc.scrabble.types.LogicalOp
And logical operation between this logical object, and another one (ScrBinary or ScrBool)
logicAnd(LogicalOp) - Method in class cl.uchile.dcc.scrabble.types.ScrBinary
Operates (logic and) this ScrBinary with the param., returning the same type as param if possible.
logicAnd(LogicalOp) - Method in class cl.uchile.dcc.scrabble.types.ScrBool
Operates (logic and) this ScrBool with the param., returning the same type as param.
